---
title: Pesto Chicken Thigh Traybake with Herby Potatoes and Caprese Salad
description: This Pesto Chicken Thigh Traybake is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pesto-chicken-thigh-traybake-ed96b6a6-2a46e6b7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/pesto-chicken-thigh-traybake-61839f3c2313ea1c304f3991-48cb7135.pdf
